data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful home situated in the heart of Visalia, CA! This stunning home boasts new carpet, paint, and light fixtures throughout, giving it a fresh and modern appeal. The newer heat/AC unit will keep you comfortable year-round.

Enjoy entertaining guests in the separate living room and family room with a cozy fireplace for those chilly evenings. Step outside to relax on one of the two large patios or utilize the RV parking for all your outdoor toys.

The lush fruit trees in the backyard provide a sweet touch to this already charming property. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of  beautiful Visalia! Schedule your showing today before it's gone!
